{
  "stem": "10825.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Philharmonic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Philharmonic, I-- I met other girls that we became friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very interesting work, because [INAUDIBLE] was a great pedagogue and a wonderful conductor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he taught us while-- while singing professional.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when-- when we gave a concert, it was-- the choir sounded like-- like a symphonic choir.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there we got acquainted with all the girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we became friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a  matter of fact, next week is coming-- his wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He passed away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's already 15-- 15 years that he passed away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his wife Rivka [INAUDIBLE] Weiner comes to visit me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She comes already the third or the fourth year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She's also a singer, and sings until today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she appears-- when she comes here she appears for Jewish organizations like YIVO, Workmen's Circle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she sings very nicely Jewish songs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and then we-- we gave concerts all over Poland that belonged to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then came a new director from Kiev to our Philharmonic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he heard the first time the choir.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He fell in love with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said that-- that such a choir has to be shown in the Soviet Union, what we have in the west, what we've found, and what work we are doing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they arranged for the 17th of June, 1941 to go to Kiev to give the first concert.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then, if we will be successful in Kiev, they'll arrange a concert in every capital of the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Life was normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't so-- we couldn't-- while I-- you see, I became the provider for the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I earned 400 rubles a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
